{"tid":1279105,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"羈留人士權利","createTime":"2019-07-02T14:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T16:10:26.000Z","uid":209225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"20c87f63638617a7f90b8011434d05d67c5adfe1","tid":1279105,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"羈留人士的權利包括：<br />\n<br />\n要求可通知親屬或朋友自己被扣留；<br />\n要求獲取律師名單；<br />\n要求申請保釋；<br />\n在要求下免費獲供應食水及足夠食物或茶點，並在有需要時獲得醫療協助；<br />\n如果不會對警方的調查工作，造成不合理延誤或阻礙、或引致司法不公，被羈留人士還應該享有以下額外權利：<br />\n<br />\n與法律顧問進行私人溝通及諮詢；<br />\n與自稱由第三者代為聘請的律師或大律師私人溝通，或拒絕與這名律師或大律師溝通；<br />\n打電話、電郵或傳真給朋友或親屬；<br />\n與警方會面時，有律師或大律師在場；<br />\n獲提供書寫用的物品；<br />\n要求在可行及盡快的情況下寄出信件，費用由被扣留人士支付；<br />\n在會面後要求在可行的情況下，獲提供警誡供詞副本，或在警誡後進行的問答紀錄副本，否則被扣留的人可以拒絕回答往後的提問；<br />\n要求提供由被扣留人士付費購買的食物或茶點。"},{"pid":"98f428a9850fe21743674f526f6d4c7e21d60c49","tid":1279105,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09459afd560e66d4bee46836c161510f1e78d513","tid":1279105,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59004a09b5ac71f25f5d0c57689c7b170963193","tid":1279105,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:16:50.000Z","msg":"新會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8aefe756a817d6cff06ef945800c7f62e49fe93","tid":1279105,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09459afd560e66d4bee46836c161510f1e78d513","tid":1279105,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}